nl.mineleni.openls.databinding.gml

Class Point

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.mineleni.openls.databinding.gml.Point
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, XmlNamespaceConstants

    public class Point
extends Object
implements XmlNamespaceConstants
    GML Point. Beschrijft het Point element uit GML 3.2.1. http://schemas.opengis.net/gml/3.2.1/geometryBasic0d1d.xsd 
     
 <complexType name="PointType">
   <complexContent>
     <extension base="gml:AbstractGeometricPrimitiveType">
       <sequence>
         <choice>
           <element ref="gml:pos" />
           <element ref="gml:coordinates" />
         </choice>
       </sequence>
     </extension>
   </complexContent>
 </complexType>
